.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, orange, grey, brown, emerald
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, argentine, dutch, brazilian, indonesian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, emeraldmaster, oliveros, baccarat, game
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, juice, iced-tea
5 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, fish, cat, rabbit

1. the russian is the person who likes chestnut
2. the argentine is the owner of the lizard
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes orange
4. the dutch is the person drinking mirinda
5. the person who likes orange is to the right of the person who likes grey
6. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the rabbit
7. the emeraldmaster-smoker is the person who likes brown
8. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle
9. the brazilian is on the far left
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle
11. the emeraldmaster-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the cat
12. the baccarat-smoker is the person drinking juice
13. the indonesian is the game-smoker
14. the brazilian is to the left or right of the person who likes emerald

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   brazilian	|    dutch	|     russian	|    argentine	|    indonesian	|
| Color		|    brown	|      emerald	|      chestnut	|     grey	|     orange	|
| Beverage	|     iced-tea	|      mirinda	|      lemonade	| juice	|     hot-chocolate	|
| Cigar		|     emeraldmaster	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| baccarat	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     turtle	|     cat	|     rabbit	|     lizard	|     fish	|
